data.description: OWNED SOLAR! Assumable 2.6% $359,000 30 year mortgage for VA buyers(Speak to your lender for details!)! Welcome to 38909 Floricita, a single-story gem nestled in Murrieta's hilltop community of Rancho Bella Vista. This single story 3 Bedroom 2 Bath 1640 sq ft home on a 5663 sq ft lot is a haven of comfort and convenience offering all the amenities of both Murrieta and Temecula (Including Temecula School district). Step inside to discover a charming floorpan that punches well above its square footage. Entering you'll immediately find a perfect placed dining nook centered around the front facing window that offers plenty of natural light into the kitchen which features plenty of storage and counter space along with with a raised bar overlooking the living room, with plenty of room for your furniture arrangement, the raised fireplace brings the entire space together. Tile floors in kitchen, bathrooms and laundry for durability and quality wood laminate for style throughout the remainder of the home, including all bedrooms! Large laundry room, complete with extra storage, adds practicality for any sized family. 3 well-sized bedrooms, including a spacious master with a walk-in closet. Master bathroom featuring dual sinks and a sleek shower stall. Outside the backyard boasts a full concrete patio slab, perimeter walkways, block wall, along with a perfect spot for garden above the full block retaining wall. Paid solar ensures an energy-efficient lifestyle, significantly lowering your electricity bills if not completely reducing them. Situated near the 15 and 215 freeways, local dining, shopping, schools and wine country, this home offers both tranquility and accessibility. The community features walking trails, parks, and award-winning schools. Make 38909 Floricita your haven – a place where comfort, convenience, and community conjoin.
